     or we may use "
    (xdoc::seetopic "apt::apt" "APT")
    " to do so.")
   (xdoc::p
    "Note that the lexical grammar for PFCS consists of a subset
     of ASCII characters that is also a subset of Unicode
     characters that UTF-8 encodes in a single byte.
